        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-euan-geddes' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0649P0_20030616_GCR_227' title='Link to this speech by Mr Euan Geddes' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-euan-geddes" title="Mr Euan Geddes">The Deputy Chairman of Committees (Lord Geddes)</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            The Committee stands adjourned until Tuesday 17th June at 3.30 p.m.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0649P0-02676'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0649P0_20030616_GCR_228' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Committee adjourned at nineteen minutes past seven o'clock.
      </p>
